n (2\u00bd) ||''<small>TBD</small>''\n|-\n| Ian Nepomniachtchi (4\u00bd) || Anish Giri (3\u00bd) ||''<small>TBD</small>''\n|-\n| Kirill Alekseenko (2\u00bd) || Alexander Grischuk (3\u00bd) ||''<small>TBD</small>''\n|-\n!colspan=3 | Round 9 &ndash; ''TBD''\n|-\n| Kirill Alekseenko (''<small>TBD</small>'') || Fabiano Caruana (''<small>TBD</small>'') ||''<small>TBD</small>''\n|-\n| Alexander Grischuk (''<small>TBD</small>'') || Ian Nepomniachtchi (''<small>TBD</small>'') ||''<small>TBD</small>''\n|-\n| Anish Giri (''<small>TBD</small>'') || Wang Hao (''<small>TBD</small>'') ||''<small>TBD</small>''\n|-\n| Ding Liren (''<small>TBD</small>'') || Maxime Vachier-Lagrave (''<small>TBD</small>'') ||''<small>TBD</small>''\n|-\n!colspan=3 | Round 10 &ndash; ''TBD''\n|-\n| Fabiano Caruana (''<small>TBD</small>'') || Ding Liren (''<small>TBD</small>'') ||''<small>TBD</small>''\n|-\n| Maxime Vachier-Lagrave (''<small>TBD</small>'') || Anish Giri (''<small>TBD</small>'') ||''<small>TBD</small>''\n|-\n| Wang Hao (''<small>TBD</small>'') || Alexander Grischuk (''<small>TBD</small>'') ||''<small>TBD</small>''\n|-\n| Ian Nepomniachtchi (''<small>TBD</small>'') || Kirill Alekseenko (''<small>TBD</small>'') ||''<small>TBD</small>''\n|-\n!colspan=3 | Round 11 &ndash; ''TBD''\n|-\n| Ian Nepomniachtchi (''<small>TBD</small>'') || Fabiano Caruana (''<small>TBD</small>'') ||''<small>TBD</small>''\n|-\n| Kirill Alekseenko (''<small>TBD</small>'') || Wang Hao (''<small>TBD</small>'') ||''<small>TBD</small>''\n|-\n| Alexander Grischuk (''<small>TBD</small>'') || Maxime Vachier-Lagrave (''<small>TBD</small>'') ||''<small>TBD</small>''\n|-\n| Anish Giri (''<small>TBD</small>'') || Ding Liren (''<small>TBD</small>'') ||''<small>TBD</small>''\n|-\n!colspan=3 | Round 12 &ndash; ''TBD''\n|-\n| Fabiano Caruana (''<small>TBD</small>'') || Anish Giri (''<small>TBD</small>'') ||''<small>TBD</small>''\n|-\n| Ding Liren (''<small>TBD</small>'') || Alexander Grischuk (''<small>TBD</small>'') ||''<small>TBD<